description: Streamlined rooms with Wi-Fi in an unpretentious hotel offering breakfast & a backup generator.
address: OLD BUSTAND, near AMBEDKAR CHOWK, Shivaji Nagar, Sangareddy, Telangana 502001, India
hotelDescription:
On a commercial street off the NH17 road, this laid-back hotel is 1 km from the Heritage Jail Museum, and 2 km from both the centre of Sangareddy and Rajiv Park.
 Featuring colourful accent walls and tiled floors, the straightforward rooms come with Wi-Fi and TVs, as well as en suite bathrooms.
 Breakfast is available and the hotel has a back-up generator.
